 */
name: SchemaHelper

comment:
/**
     * Gets a list of native schema objects
     *
     * @returns {Promise} Array of Schemas
     */

name: getNativeSchemas

comment:
/**
     * Gets a list of all custom schema objects
     *
     * @param {String} project
     * @param {String} environment
     *
     * @returns {Promise} Array of Schemas
     */

name: getCustomSchemas

comment:
/**
     * Gets a list of all schema objects
     *
     * @param {String} project
     * @param {String} environment
     *
     * @returns {Promise} Array of Schemas
     */

name: getAllSchemas

comment:
/**
     * Checks whether a Schema id belongs to a native schema
     *
     * @param {String} id
     *
     * @returns {Boolean} isNative
     */

name: isNativeSchema

comment:
/**
     * Gets a native Schema by id
     *
     * @param {String} id
     *
     * @returns {Promise} Schema
     */

name: getNativeSchema

comment:
/**
     * Gets a Schema by id
     *
     * @param {String} project
     * @param {String} environment

     *
     * @return {Promise} Schema
     */

comment:
/**
     * Gets all parent fields
     *

     * @returns {Promise} Schema with all aprent fields
     */
name: getSchemaWithParentFields

     * Removes a Schema object by id

     */

comment:

     * @param {String} newId
     *
     * @return {Promise} Check result
     */
description: Checks if a Schema is being updated with an id that already exists
name: duplicateIdCheck
